  $( Adding a multiple of one operand of the ` gcd ` operator to the other does
     not alter the result.  (Contributed by Paul Chapman, 31-Mar-2011.) $)
  gcdaddm $p |- ( ( K e. ZZ /\ M e. ZZ /\ N e. ZZ ) ->
                  ( M gcd N ) = ( M gcd ( N + ( K x. M ) ) ) ) $=
