    OUNVTVLVGULVOUMVTVLHVPUQBPUGVQUKQTUIUJ $.
    $( [31-Mar-2011] $)

  $( The gcd remains unchanged if one operand is replaced with its remainder
     modulo the other.  (Contributed by Paul Chapman, 31-Mar-2011.) $)
